  "text": "The list shows that the identified perceived chances and risks of the potential futures of a concrete technology are largely systemic and that interactions between the features of this complex technology are considered in their social context [CITATION_1] . One example is the intensive debate among citizens on the risk of exclusion of people by using the technology in public spaces.",
